---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { images } from '../data/images';
---

<Layout>
  <slot name="head">
    <title>Location — The Meridian Residences | Kebayoran Baru, South Jakarta</title>
    <meta name="description" content="The Meridian Residences occupies a prestigious address in Kebayoran Baru, South Jakarta's most coveted enclave — minutes from SCBD, Plaza Senayan, and Pacific Place." />
  </slot>

  <!-- Hero Mini -->
  <section class="pt-48 pb-24 bg-primary-black">
    <div class="container-standard text-center reveal">
      <p class="overline mb-4"><span class="lang-en">Location</span><span class="lang-id">Lokasi</span></p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-primary-ivory leading-tight mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">The Address — Kebayoran Baru</span><span class="lang-id">Alamat — Kebayoran Baru</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="lang-en text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        The Meridian Residences stands in the heart of Kebayoran Baru, South Jakarta's most enduring prestigious
        enclave. Here, tree-lined avenues, diplomatic quarters, and international institutions converge to create
        an address of quiet distinction — where every convenience is within reach and every arrival feels like a
        homecoming.
      </p>
      <p class="lang-id text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        The Meridian Residences berdiri di jantung Kebayoran Baru, enklave prestisius paling abadi di Jakarta
        Selatan. Di sini, jalanan rindang, kawasan diplomatik, dan institusi internasional bertemu menciptakan
        sebuah alamat dengan kemuliaan yang tenang — di mana setiap kemudahan dalam jangkauan dan setiap
        kedatangan terasa seperti pulang ke rumah.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Location Banner Image -->
  <img src={images.location.neighborhood} alt={images.location.neighborhoodAlt} class="w-full h-64 md:h-96 object-cover rounded-sm mt-8" />

  <!-- Neighborhood Narrative -->
  <section class="bg-primary-black">
    <div class="container-standard reveal">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="overline mb-6"><span class="lang-en">The Neighborhood</span><span class="lang-id">Kawasan Sekitar</span></p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-primary-ivory mb-8"><span class="lang-en">South Jakarta's Most Coveted Enclave</span><span class="lang-id">Enklave Paling Didambakan Jakarta Selatan</span></h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
          <p class="lang-en">
            Kebayoran Baru occupies a singular position in Jakarta's urban geography. Conceived in the 1950s as the city's
            first planned satellite town — a "garden city" in the grand tradition — it has evolved across seven decades into
            the archipelago's most desirable residential address.
          </p>
          <p class="lang-id">
            Kebayoran Baru menempati posisi tunggal dalam geografi urban Jakarta. Diciptakan pada tahun 1950-an sebagai
            kota satelit terencana pertama — sebuah "kota taman" dalam tradisi megah — kawasan ini telah berkembang selama
            tujuh dekade menjadi alamat hunian paling didambakan di nusantara.
          </p>
          <p class="lang-en">
            What distinguishes Kebayoran Baru from every other precinct in the city is the density of institutional
            validation it has accumulated: the international schools, the private hospitals, the diplomatic compounds, the
            private members' clubs. These are not amenities that can be built overnight. They are the product of decades of
            sustained investment — and they create a neighborhood that continues to appreciate, in every sense of the word.
          </p>
          <p class="lang-id">
            Yang membedakan Kebayoran Baru dari setiap kawasan lain di kota ini adalah kepadatan validasi institusional
            yang telah terakumulasi: sekolah internasional, rumah sakit swasta, kompleks diplomatik, klub anggota pribadi.
            Ini bukanlah fasilitas yang dapat dibangun dalam semalam. Mereka adalah hasil dari investasi berkelanjutan
            selama puluhan tahun — dan menciptakan kawasan yang terus terapresiasi, dalam setiap arti kata.
          </p>
          <p class="lang-en">
            For residents of The Meridian, this translates into something tangible: a life lived within minutes of
            everything that matters, surrounded by the mature tree canopies and generous green spaces that remain
            the neighborhood's most precious inheritance.
          </p>
          <p class="lang-id">
            Bagi penghuni The Meridian, ini berarti sesuatu yang nyata: kehidupan yang dijalani dalam hitungan menit dari
            segala hal yang penting, dikelilingi oleh kanopi pohon dewasa dan ruang hijau yang luas yang tetap menjadi
            warisan paling berharga kawasan ini.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Landmark Proximity Cards -->
  <section class="bg-primary-black">
    <div class="container-standard reveal">
      <p class="overline mb-6"><span class="lang-en">Proximity</span><span class="lang-id">Kedekatan</span></p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-primary-ivory mb-12"><span class="lang-en">Landmarks Within Reach</span><span class="lang-id">Tengara Dalam Jangkauan</span></h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Plaza Senayan -->
        <div class="bg-primary-charcoal border border-primary-ivory/5 rounded-sm p-8 card-lift">
          <h4 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-primary-ivory mb-2">Plaza Senayan</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gold font-medium mb-3">~10 minutes</p>
          <p class="lang-en text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            An iconic destination for luxury retail, fine dining, and premium entertainment in the heart of South Jakarta.
          </p>
          <p class="lang-id text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Destinasi ikonik untuk ritel mewah, santapan fine dining, dan hiburan premium di jantung Jakarta Selatan.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Pacific Place -->
        <div class="bg-primary-charcoal border border-primary-ivory/5 rounded-sm p-8 card-lift">
          <h4 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-primary-ivory mb-2">Pacific Place</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gold font-medium mb-3">~12 minutes</p>
          <p class="lang-en text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            A premium shopping and lifestyle destination connected to the Ritz-Carlton Jakarta, in the heart of the SCBD.
          </p>
          <p class="lang-id text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Destinasi belanja dan gaya hidup premium yang terhubung dengan Ritz-Carlton Jakarta, di jantung SCBD.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- SCBD -->
        <div class="bg-primary-charcoal border border-primary-ivory/5 rounded-sm p-8 card-lift">
          <h4 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-primary-ivory mb-2">SCBD</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gold font-medium mb-3">~8 minutes</p>
          <p class="lang-en text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Southeast Asia's most concentrated financial precinct — home to global corporations, five-star hotels, and the Jakarta Stock Exchange.
          </p>
          <p class="lang-id text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Kawasan finansial paling terkonsentrasi di Asia Tenggara — rumah bagi korporasi global, hotel bintang lima, dan Bursa Efek Jakarta.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Pondok Indah -->
        <div class="bg-primary-charcoal border border-primary-ivory/5 rounded-sm p-8 card-lift">
          <h4 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-primary-ivory mb-2">Pondok Indah</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gold font-medium mb-3">~15 minutes</p>
          <p class="lang-en text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            An established upscale residential area offering premium shopping malls, international hospitals, and golf courses.
          </p>
          <p class="lang-id text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Kawasan hunian mapan kelas atas yang menawarkan pusat perbelanjaan premium, rumah sakit internasional, dan lapangan golf.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Soekarno-Hatta -->
        <div class="bg-primary-charcoal border border-primary-ivory/5 rounded-sm p-8 card-lift">
          <h4 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-primary-ivory mb-2">Soekarno-Hatta International</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gold font-medium mb-3">~45 minutes</p>
          <p class="lang-en text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Indonesia's primary international gateway, connecting Jakarta to major cities across Asia, the Middle East, and beyond.
          </p>
          <p class="lang-id text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Gerbang internasional utama Indonesia, menghubungkan Jakarta ke kota-kota besar di seluruh Asia, Timur Tengah, dan sekitarnya.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Connectivity -->
  <section class="bg-primary-black">
    <div class="container-standard reveal">
      <p class="overline mb-6"><span class="lang-en">Connectivity</span><span class="lang-id">Konektivitas</span></p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-primary-ivory mb-8"><span class="lang-en">Effortlessly Connected</span><span class="lang-id">Terhubung Tanpa Hambatan</span></h2>
      <p class="lang-en text-lg text-neutral-300 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
        The Meridian benefits from direct access to Jakarta's principal arterial roads, including Jalan Sudirman and
        the inner-city toll network. The recently completed MRT North-South line places the entire city within effortless
        reach, while Soekarno-Hatta International Airport is accessible in well under an hour — a threshold that makes
        The Meridian a viable primary residence for the internationally mobile professional.
      </p>
      <p class="lang-id text-lg text-neutral-300 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
        The Meridian menikmati akses langsung ke jalan arteri utama Jakarta, termasuk Jalan Sudirman dan jaringan tol
        dalam kota. Jalur MRT Utara-Selatan yang baru saja selesai menempatkan seluruh kota dalam jangkauan tanpa
        hambatan, sementara Bandara Internasional Soekarno-Hatta dapat diakses dalam waktu kurang dari satu jam —
        ambang batas yang menjadikan The Meridian hunian utama yang layak bagi profesional yang mobile secara
        internasional.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Neighborhood Guide -->
  <section class="bg-primary-black">
    <div class="container-standard reveal">
      <p class="overline mb-6"><span class="lang-en">Neighborhood Guide</span><span class="lang-id">Panduan Kawasan</span></p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-primary-ivory mb-12"><span class="lang-en">A Curated Guide to the Area</span><span class="lang-id">Panduan Kurasi Kawasan</span></h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-primary-charcoal border border-primary-ivory/5 rounded-sm p-6 card-lift">
          <h4 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-gold mb-4"><span class="lang-en">Dining</span><span class="lang-id">Bersantap</span></h4>
          <p class="lang-en text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            From fine dining establishments to neighborhood bistros, a world of culinary excellence awaits within minutes
            of The Meridian. South Jakarta's dining scene is among the most dynamic in Southeast Asia.
          </p>
          <p class="lang-id text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Dari restoran fine dining hingga bistro lingkungan, dunia keunggulan kuliner menanti dalam hitungan menit
            dari The Meridian. Dunia kuliner Jakarta Selatan termasuk yang paling dinamis di Asia Tenggara.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-primary-charcoal border border-primary-ivory/5 rounded-sm p-6 card-lift">
          <h4 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-gold mb-4"><span class="lang-en">Shopping</span><span class="lang-id">Belanja</span></h4>
          <p class="lang-en text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Premium malls and curated boutiques line the nearby avenues — offering everything from international luxury
            houses to Indonesian design ateliers and artisan markets.
          </p>
          <p class="lang-id text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Mal premium dan butik kurasi berjejer di sepanjang jalan terdekat — menawarkan segalanya dari rumah mode
            mewah internasional hingga atelier desain Indonesia dan pasar artisan.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-primary-charcoal border border-primary-ivory/5 rounded-sm p-6 card-lift">
          <h4 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-gold mb-4"><span class="lang-en">Culture</span><span class="lang-id">Budaya</span></h4>
          <p class="lang-en text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Galleries, museums, and performance spaces are woven through the neighborhood fabric — a reflection of Jakarta's
            growing cultural confidence and creative energy.
          </p>
          <p class="lang-id text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Galeri, museum, dan ruang pertunjukan terjalin di seluruh struktur kawasan — cerminan dari kepercayaan
            diri budaya dan energi kreatif Jakarta yang terus berkembang.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-primary-charcoal border border-primary-ivory/5 rounded-sm p-6 card-lift">
          <h4 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-gold mb-4"><span class="lang-en">Education</span><span class="lang-id">Pendidikan</span></h4>
          <p class="lang-en text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Internationally accredited schools — including British, American, and IB curriculum institutions — are located
            within the immediate vicinity, serving families who demand the highest educational standards.
          </p>
          <p class="lang-id text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Sekolah terakreditasi internasional — termasuk institusi kurikulum Inggris, Amerika, dan IB — berlokasi
            di sekitar kawasan, melayani keluarga yang menuntut standar pendidikan tertinggi.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-primary-charcoal border border-primary-ivory/5 rounded-sm p-6 card-lift">
          <h4 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-gold mb-4"><span class="lang-en">Healthcare</span><span class="lang-id">Kesehatan</span></h4>
          <p class="lang-en text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            JCI-accredited hospitals with comprehensive specialist services — including emergency, maternity, and
            executive health screening — are within close proximity.
          </p>
          <p class="lang-id text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Rumah sakit terakreditasi JCI dengan layanan spesialis komprehensif — termasuk darurat, persalinan, dan
            pemeriksaan kesehatan eksekutif — berada dalam jarak dekat.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Map CTA -->
  <section class="bg-primary-black">
    <div class="container-standard text-center reveal">
      <div class="bg-primary-midnight rounded-sm p-16">
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-primary-ivory mb-6"><span class="lang-en">Find Your Way</span><span class="lang-id">Temukan Jalan Anda</span></h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-neutral-300 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Visit our Sales Gallery to experience the neighborhood firsthand and discover why Kebayoran Baru remains
          the address of choice for those who understand what location truly means.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact#visit" class="btn btn-outline-gold btn-lg" data-lang-en="View on Map" data-lang-id="Lihat di Peta">View on Map</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
